<data key="n_definition">A subdivision of the digestive tract in humans that includes the rectum, the anal canal and the anus. | The distal portion of the gastrointestinal tract that includes the anal canal and rectum.</data>
<data key="n_aliases">Anorectal Area|ANORECTUM|Anorectum|anorectum</data>
<data key="n_nci_url">https://ncit.nci.nih.gov/ncitbrowser/ConceptReport.jsp?dictionary=NCI_Thesaurus&amp;ns=ncit&amp;code=C186102</data>
