<data key="n_umls_cui">C1705966</data>
<data key="n_definition">Human CDH1 wild-type allele is located in the vicinity of 16q22.1 and is approximately 98 kb in length. This allele, which encodes cadherin-1 protein, plays a role in cell-cell adhesion and cell-matrix adhesion.</data>
