<data key="n_umls_cui">C1706153</data>
<data key="n_definition">Human CEACAM7 wild-type allele is located in the vicinity of 19q13.2 and is approximately 15 kb in length. This allele, which encodes carcinoembryonic antigen-related cell adhesion molecule 7 protein, is involved in tumor suppression and cellular growth.</data>
