<data key="n_umls_cui">C1880659</data>
<data key="n_definition">A regimen comsisting of 5-fluorouracil, leucovorin and oxaliplatin, given on a 14-day cycle, that can be used for the treatment of ampullary and pancreatic adenocarcinoma, and biliary tract, esophageal and esophagogastric junction, gastric, and colorectal cancers.</data>
