<node id="C12615">
<data key="n_label">Glial Cell</data>
<data key="n_node_kind">Entity</data>
<data key="n_in_colorectal_tree">N</data>
<data key="n_category">Cell</data>
<data key="n_research_axis">Pathology/cytology</data>
<data key="n_semantic_types">Cell</data>
<data key="n_umls_cui">C0027836</data>
<data key="n_definition">A non-neuronal cell of the nervous system. Glial cells have diverse roles, including in regulation of neuronal survival and differentiation, maintenance of ion and neurotransmitter concentrations in the neuronal environment, synapse formation, and support of synaptic interactions and electrical signal propagation. | Any of the cells that hold nerve cells in place and help them work the way they should. The types of neuroglia include oligodendrocytes, astrocytes, microglia, and ependymal cells.</data>
<data key="n_aliases">Glia|Glial Cell|glial cell|Glial Cells|Kolliker Reticulum|neuroglia|Neuroglia|Neuroglial Cell|Neuroglial Cells</data>
<data key="n_nci_url">https://ncit.nci.nih.gov/ncitbrowser/ConceptReport.jsp?dictionary=NCI_Thesaurus&amp;ns=ncit&amp;code=C12615</data>
</node>
<node id="C201135">
<data key="n_label">Goblet Cell Adenocarcinoma</data>
<data key="n_node_kind">Entity</data>
<data key="n_in_colorectal_tree">N</data>
<data key="n_category">Associated Disease/Neoplasm</data>
<data key="n_research_axis">Associated conditions</data>
<data key="n_semantic_types">Neoplastic Process</data>
<data key="n_umls_cui">C0205695</data>
<data key="n_definition">A rare adenocarcinoma of the digestive system that exhibits neuroendocrine differentiation and is associated with the presence of neoplastic signet-ring cells resembling goblet cells of the intestine.</data>
<data key="n_aliases">Adenocarcinoid tumor|Adenocarcinoid Tumor|Composite carcinoid|Digestive System Goblet Cell Adenocarcinoma|GCA|Goblet Cell Adenocarcinoma|Goblet Cell Carcinoid</data>
<data key="n_nci_url">https://ncit.nci.nih.gov/ncitbrowser/ConceptReport.jsp?dictionary=NCI_Thesaurus&amp;ns=ncit&amp;code=C201135</data>
</node>
<node id="C28077">
<data key="n_label">Grade 1</data>
