<data key="n_definition">A morphologic qualifier indicating that a cancerous lesion is moderately differentiated.</data>
<data key="n_aliases">2|G2|G2 Intermediate Grade|G2 Moderately differentiated|Grade 2|Grade II|Intermediate Grade|Medium|Moderately Differentiated|Moderately Well Differentiated</data>
