<data key="n_definition">Human RAD54L wild-type allele is located within 1p32 and is approximately 31 kb in length. This allele, which encodes DNA repair and recombination protein RAD54-like protein, is involved in the homologous recombination related repair of DNA double-strand breaks.</data>
<data key="n_aliases">hHR54|HR54|HR54 Gene|hRAD54|HRAD54 Gene|RAD54 (S.cerevisiae)-Like Gene|RAD54 Homolog Gene|RAD54, S.cerevisiae, Homolog-Like Gene|RAD54-like (S. cerevisiae) wt Allele|RAD54-Like Protein Gene|RAD54A|RAD54L wt Allele</data>
