<data key="n_semantic_types">Tissue</data>
<data key="n_umls_cui">C0040300</data>
<data key="n_definition">A group or layer of cells that work together to perform a specific function. | An anatomical structure consisting of similarly specialized cells and intercellular matrix, aggregated according to genetically determined spatial relationships, performing a specific function. | An anatomical structure consisting of similarly specialized cells and intercellular matrix, aggregated according to genetically determined spatial relationships, performing a specific function. (NCI)</data>
